g class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/747320/extras/32cf7d7723247aa8844ac50d6c5ba5df.avif?t=1535585489\" width=615 height=135 /></span><br><br>Face your personal heroic adventure in a dangerously beautiful world of Bravium.",
